# Official certification-body logos go here (committed to git so they deploy).
#
# Drop transparent-background PNG or SVG files named exactly:
#   scaled-agile.png   (or .svg)   — Scaled Agile / SAFe
#   pmi.png                          — Project Management Institute
#   scrum-alliance.png               — Scrum Alliance
#   axelos.png                       — AXELOS (ITIL / PRINCE2)
#   iiba.png                         — IIBA
#   icagile.png                      — ICAgile
#   peoplecert.png                   — PeopleCert
#
# Source each from the body's official partner/accreditation resource kit.
# Until a file exists, the homepage shows a clean text wordmark fallback.
